00:32:11.910 --> 00:32:15.060
You may be familiar that the ACC/AHA is now releasing

768
00:32:15.060 --> 00:32:18.570
or has just rolled out a brand new risk calculator.

769
00:32:18.570 --> 00:32:19.770
It's called PREVENT

770
00:32:19.770 --> 00:32:22.890
and I honestly forget what the acronym stands for.

771
00:32:22.890 --> 00:32:24.960
It is a huge improvement

772
00:32:24.960 --> 00:32:28.080
over the current ASCVD risk calculator.

